"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-quincy-hall-comeback-gold-400-meters\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Quincy Hall appeared to be languishing through most of the 400-meter sprint Wednesday night at the Stade de France, then he found another gear.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9999432879651264, \"rank\": 4.166537504177162e-05, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hall authored one of the more remarkable comebacks of the 2024 Summer Olympics to take home gold in the 400 meters.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He entered the final straightaway deep in the field, in a distant fourth place and somehow worked his way through the field to find victory.\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The video has to be seen to be believed.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NEVER doubt Quincy Hall.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9999432879651264, \"rank\": 4.166537504177162e-05, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00b1A EPIC comeback to win 400m GOLD!#ParisOlympics\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0093\\u00ba NBC & Peacockpic.twitter.com/qQJqfxrH9n  Just an incredible kick.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epic_Records\", \"score\": 0.999872136939942, \"rank\": 0.00012721568806000428, \"text\": \"EPIC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epic_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epic_Records\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It looked like Hall was running and everyone else was jogging.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 300-meter mark, it appeared Great Britain's Matthew Hudson-Smith and Trinidad and Tobago's Jereem Richards would battle it out for gold, but Zambia's Muzala Samukonga charged late.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999571138772813, \"rank\": 4.120063703231991e-05, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Hudson-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hudson-Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"score\": 0.9997330506459084, \"rank\": 0.0002670007955094087, \"text\": \"Trinidad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\"}, {\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jereem_Richards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jereem Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jereem_Richards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jereem_Richards\"}, {\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_